      "text": "class FooService : ServiceBase {\n\n  // YOU implement this:\n  virtual int handleGetData(\n    uint32_t id,\n    SensorData &data) = 0;\n\n  // Generated for you:\n  void notifyOnUpdate(\n    const SensorData &data);\n\nprivate:\n  void onRequest(...) override;\n};",
