      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "class FooClient : ClientBase {\n\n  // Generated typed RPC:\n  int GetData(\n    uint32_t id,\n    SensorData &data,\n    int timeoutMs = 2000);\n\n  // YOU implement this:\n  virtual void onOnUpdate(\n    const SensorData &data) {}\n\nprivate:\n  void onNotification(...) override;\n};",
