      "seed": 14003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 14004, "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1774700000000, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "The \"magic\": Write the IDL once → ipcgen generates all marshaling, dispatch, and RPC correlation code.\n\nServer developer: subclass FooService, implement handleGetData(). Call notifyOnUpdate() to broadcast.\nClient developer: create FooClient, call GetData(id, data). Override onOnUpdate() for notifications.\nNo manual serialization, no protocol knowledge, no ring buffer management. Just typed function calls.",
      "originalText": "The \"magic\": Write the IDL once → ipcgen generates all marshaling, dispatch, and RPC correlation code.\n\nServer developer: subclass FooService, implement handleGetData(). Call notifyOnUpdate() to broadcast.\nClient developer: create FooClient, call GetData(id, data). Override onOnUpdate() for notifications.\nNo manual serialization, no protocol knowledge, no ring buffer management. Just typed function calls.",
      "autoResize": true, "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle", "containerId": "summary", "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
